WEBVTT

00:02:29.863 --> 00:02:31.276
If you pollute here,

00:02:31.300 --> 00:02:36.093
it's going to affect it when the rain
comes to my country.

00:02:36.981 --> 00:02:41.537
I used to say we all belong
to the global village.

00:02:41.561 --> 00:02:45.942
I used to say, Amazon belongs to humanity,

00:02:45.966 --> 00:02:51.816
and also that humanity needs to take care
as the indigenous do in the world.

00:02:52.776 --> 00:02:55.504
And for this reason,

00:02:56.474 --> 00:03:01.966
today is a time to wake, unite us.